Touch Screen Mode

Touch Zoom


If the lens supports touch zoom, you can zoom in and out by touching the display. Tap the touch zoom button in the display to enable touch zoom.区 popper⌀ ZOOM ZOOM
Touch zoom is controlled using the but- tons in the display.수 ㉶ へ T papplept w II = x

1

ButtonDescription
ZOOMTouch zoomEnable touch zoom.
TZoom inZoom in or out. Touch and hold to zoom in or out at a constant speed.
wZoom out
스Rocker switchThe camera zooms in or out at a speed corresponding to the position of the rocker switch.
こ
XDisableDisable touch zoom.

The rate at which the camera zooms in and out in response to the T
and W buttons can be selected using 8 BUTTON/DIAL SETTING >
LENS ZOOM/FOCUS SETTING > CONSTANT SPEED ZOOM (Fn).

# Touch Zoom

| --- | --- |
| Touch zoom is controlled using the but- tons in the display. | 수 ㉶ へ T papplept w II = x |


1

| Button | Button | Description |
| --- | --- | --- |
| ZOOM | Touch zoom | Enable touch zoom. |
| T | Zoom in | Zoom in or out. Touch and hold to zoom in or out at a constant speed. |
| w | Zoom out | Zoom in or out. Touch and hold to zoom in or out at a constant speed. |
| 스 | Rocker switch | The camera zooms in or out at a speed corresponding to the position of the rocker switch. |
|  | Rocker switch | The camera zooms in or out at a speed corresponding to the position of the rocker switch. |
|  | Rocker switch | The camera zooms in or out at a speed corresponding to the position of the rocker switch. |
| こ | Rocker switch | The camera zooms in or out at a speed corresponding to the position of the rocker switch. |
| X | Disable | Disable touch zoom. |


The rate at which the camera zooms in and out in response to the T
and W buttons can be selected using 8 BUTTON/DIAL SETTING >
LENS ZOOM/FOCUS SETTING > CONSTANT SPEED ZOOM (Fn).
